---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About Latinium.ai"
  description="Learn about Latinium.ai, our mission, and how we're making Latin language analysis accessible and engaging."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-12 text-center">
      About Latinium.ai
    </h1>

    <div class="glass-panel p-8 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Latinium.ai was born from a passion for classical languages and a vision
        to make Latin analysis more accessible and engaging to everyone. Our
        platform combines modern technology with classical education to create
        an intuitive and powerful tool for exploring Latin texts.
      </p>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">
        Powered by custom AI, Latinium.ai helps users understand complex
        grammatical structures and relationships through dynamic visual
        representations. Whether you're a student tackling Latin for the first
        time, an educator seeking better teaching tools, or a scholar conducting
        research, our platform provides valuable insights that enhance
        comprehension and appreciation of Latin texts.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="glass-panel p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Key Technologies</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-300 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Astro framework for fast, optimized web performance</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-300 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Interactive visualizations with D3.js</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-300 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Custom AI for advanced language processing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-300 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Modern UI with TailwindCSS</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-panel p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Who It's For</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-300 mr-2 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span
              ><strong>Students</strong> - Visual learning tools to supplement textbook
